title: Design your Kitchen with Visio and display it in 3D with SharpGL OpenGL library.
sortTitle: design your kitchen with visio and display it in 3d with sharpgl opengl library.
description: In this session we will show you how you can use Visio to create your Kitchen and viewing it in 3D. A specific VSTO Addin has been build to design, produce plan and quotation. you can also view it in 3D thanks to the usage of SharpGL (Open GL based) 3d graphic library.You will learn	1. The basics of creating a C# Visio VSTO Addin with automatic database storage of Visio Shapes	2. The basic of SharGL Library	3. How you can create your kitchen IKEA based furniture	4. Experiment the viewing of your kitchen in 3D.
